The CasparCG builds site at [http://casparcg.com/builds/CasparCG%20Server/ http://builds.casparcg.com] contains pre-compiled versios of the Caspar CG Server 2.1 source code, if you wish to build it yourself, some notes can be found below, for more detail please search the [http://casparcg.com/forum forums].



==System Requirements==

* 64bit OS (Windows 7 64bit is preferred)
* 64bit Flash Player http://aihdownload.adobe.com/bin/live/install_flashplayer11x32ax_mssd_aih.exe

==Setup==

# Download and unzip current version of CasparCG
# Copy the server folder somewhere
# Download and unzip current alpha from http://builds.casparcg.com/
# Copy all files from the alpha over the files in your server folder
# Delete all cg20.fth... files


